      <title>日本制药商正在调查有毒药丸导致死亡人数增加的情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/japan-drugmaker-looking-into-higher-death-count-from-toxic-pills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小林制药公司正在调查是否有 76 人因服用含有红曲的保健品而死亡，这个数字高于最初报道的死亡人数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/japan-drugmaker-looking-into-higher-death-count-from-toxic-pills</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 06:52:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储转向将增强印度相对于新兴市场的收益率优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/fed-pivot-seen-boosting-india-s-yield-advantage-over-em-peers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[普信集团 (T. Rowe Price Group Inc.) 表示，一旦美联储和其他央行开始降息，流入印度 1.3 万亿美元主权债券市场的外国资金可能会增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/fed-pivot-seen-boosting-india-s-yield-advantage-over-em-peers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 06:52:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度计划简化全球基金购买其债券的繁琐手续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/india-plans-to-cut-red-tape-for-global-funds-buying-its-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，随着印度首次被纳入国际债券指数，印度资本市场监管机构正努力减少外国投资者仅购买主权债务的文书工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/india-plans-to-cut-red-tape-for-global-funds-buying-its-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 06:47:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国通胀在选举前两天恢复放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/french-inflation-resumes-slowdown-two-days-before-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国通胀略有放缓 — — 这强化了欧洲央行开始削减历史高利率的决定，并为总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙在选举前两天带来了经济亮点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/french-inflation-resumes-slowdown-two-days-before-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 06:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥央行行长罗德里格斯暗示仍有进一步降息的“空间”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/banxico-governor-rodriguez-signals-openness-to-more-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥央行行长维多利亚·罗德里格斯表示，比索的波动影响了央行周四维持利率不变的决定。鉴于其可能对通胀产生影响，它也可能影响央行如何权衡未来的降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/banxico-governor-rodriguez-signals-openness-to-more-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 00:41:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本东证指数创 1990 年以来最高盘中水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/japan-s-benchmark-topix-stock-index-is-heading-for-1990-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本东证指数周五触及 1990 年以来的最高水平，随后回吐部分涨幅，因提高股东回报的努力以及受益于更高利率的金融股支撑了这一股票基准指数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/japan-s-benchmark-topix-stock-index-is-heading-for-1990-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 00:17:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
