    <item>
      <title>欧莱雅预计中国市场增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/l-oreal-ceo-sees-slower-beauty-market-growth-as-china-struggles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧莱雅公司首席执行官表示，预计今年整体美容市场的增长将放缓，因为在经历了多年的快速增长之后，中国市场的疲软对销售额造成了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/l-oreal-ceo-sees-slower-beauty-market-growth-as-china-struggles</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 16:46:10 GMT</pubDate>
